{"tid":2413132,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"波多野結衣面癱狂標眼水要停工　堅強背後11個經歷讓她炮灰變女神","createTime":"2021-02-18T12:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T13:24:10.000Z","uid":117934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"78e2ff2c28759793a2ebd3dfe70301315bfadf63","tid":2413132,"uid":117934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:54:03.000Z","msg":"日本AV女優波多野結衣日前在Twitter發文懷疑自己面癱，左邊臉郁唔到，連眼也合不上，所有工作都要暫停，情況令人擔心。一代女優會否就此告別AV影圈，尚是未知之數。<br />\n<br />\n作為日本當紅的AV女優，波多野結衣都是經過一輪艱苦努力，才能走到今天。她最初在日本只是一個二三線小角色，全因一個舉動，令她在海外爆紅，更反攻日本。究竟她如何在競爭激烈的環境下長期企穩？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210216/438329093398728704876901.png/dSrsQRV_i3zB5zFNKjvVYXV5ASBTyM2_PyQXjT8kF40?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210216%2F438329093398728704876901.png%2FdSrsQRV_i3zB5zFNKjvVYXV5ASBTyM2_PyQXjT8kF40%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=56e2c797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本AV女優波多野結衣人氣一直高企，不過最近她在Twitter表示面部不適，診斷疑似「顏面神經麻痺」，舌頭有麻痹感，只有右邊面郁到，左眼無法緊閉，令對眼好乾不停流眼淚，而左邊鼻孔亦無法控制鼻水流出。波多野結衣指自己正接受類固醇治療，亦因此導致免疫力變低要留家休養。她表示雖然痛苦會令自己變得更堅強，但獨自在家時仍因難受而忍不住痛哭，令不少粉絲擔心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1359809907634040839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1359809907634040839&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69BphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=6b5de523\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1359809907634040839&h=fac9705e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/i/status/1359809907634040839</a>"},{"pid":"59fd396fa2fbd0a11f38a2ba8eb539688f64f684","tid":2413132,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:00:51.000Z","msg":"面癱，武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1efb8759b8f8aac76baf99a822707dd07197b69","tid":2413132,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:03:45.000Z","msg":"可能有男優啲精有病毒, 一顏射就..."},{"pid":"90901d3ba332b7c8da255b521236c3e4045643ae","tid":2413132,"uid":117934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vv4RkSh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvv4RkSh.jpg&h=0b29bfd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c929317ecc2148330c03ee1ccc26eb8a5ee173c6","tid":2413132,"uid":205099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:24:10.000Z","msg":"爲咗俾支那人包養去整容，抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}